{"tid":2273114,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"激光矯視做唔做好？有冇人分享吓","createTime":"2020-11-05T13:27:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T16:23:20.000Z","uid":364899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5b30b6b05684a9fcbf23a318ebe4c29fb96e81a3","tid":2273114,"uid":364899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:27:14.000Z","msg":"一隻左眼400幾度，右500 度。一除眼鏡淨係見到一隻手嘅距離，平時返工係帶one day con ，但係最近隻眼好唔舒服，好乾。有衝動想做激光但係好驚會唔會手術失敗而盲咗？"},{"pid":"0727b9e00bd8328761d18f6bf7ed532d6be2069f","tid":2273114,"uid":68553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:33:00.000Z","msg":"係都做smile啦,去養和做"},{"pid":"c7532c9179c620a700ae85fd8ca4433d5e9b2e1f","tid":2273114,"uid":364899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0727b9e00bd8328761d18f6bf7ed532d6be2069f","tid":2273114,"uid":68553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:33:00.000Z","msg":"係都做smile啦,去養和做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T15:30:33.000Z","msg":"養和係咪安全D？"},{"pid":"7fcbbd0cd517b76ee8413435fa491c646e7838f5","tid":2273114,"uid":110852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T01:01:48.000Z","msg":"盲又難d<br />\n最多做完都有度數/仲眼乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ca40d57ad00c6aa0eabe97843ef90b88fdcc5f","tid":2273114,"uid":323955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fcbbd0cd517b76ee8413435fa491c646e7838f5","tid":2273114,"uid":110852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T01:01:48.000Z","msg":"盲又難d<br />\n最多做完都有度數/仲眼乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T03:14:05.000Z","msg":"咁就放心，我好驚盲咗"},{"pid":"3bc33c3de007f155781210a452c7f415c1da88d8","tid":2273114,"uid":323955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T03:18:27.000Z","msg":"我打算下個月都去做。我都同屋企人講會唔會盲。 同你諗法一樣"},{"pid":"7cbd6b05aa645436b04dc65dfb8856a7020a3c87","tid":2273114,"uid":121286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T03:21:09.000Z","msg":"之前唔係有人開po話做完勁多飛蚊咩？"},{"pid":"5f60e45791884dd9f9c2a3f446bf9c4837ea05dd","tid":2273114,"uid":110852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cbd6b05aa645436b04dc65dfb8856a7020a3c87","tid":2273114,"uid":121286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T03:21:09.000Z","msg":"之前唔係有人開po話做完勁多飛蚊咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T05:29:51.000Z","msg":"都無搞到你個視網膜<br />\n淨係開cornea點整到你飛蚊啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f53598b9718c2b9fa254d80239c638bbec02f278","tid":2273114,"uid":171409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T06:52:51.000Z","msg":"做左年幾 smile<br />\n做完精神好多，完全冇問題 <br />\n果陣中環做做兩萬幾 <br />\n可以去聽左講座先 聽下醫生介紹<br />\n同檢查適唔適合做先"},{"pid":"b9297602dab9f79b39b96e1d9654c6312793ab37","tid":2273114,"uid":41302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T07:07:54.000Z","msg":"我400/350近視 散光應該百零<br />\n<br />\n半年前係清X做左SMILE <br />\n做完過左幾分鐘已經覺得係睇野清左但就有層白霧咁 <br />\n番屋企即刻訓 訓醒睇野已經無乜問題白霧消失左小小<br />\n頭一星期要瘋狂滴佢D藥水 一星期之後白霧無左<br />\n對上一次覆診驗眼都仲係話我0近視+散光"},{"pid":"d783feb7f9d0673131234d443f05c14527f656e9","tid":2273114,"uid":26270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:41:16.000Z","msg":"做咗lasik<br />\n500近視 250散光<br />\n第1日辛苦啲 第2日基本清哂 但望光有光暈(醫生話會退)<br />\n但lasik護理真係麻煩啲 勁驚整到個flap移位<br />\nsmile係冇咁快清+冇追蹤眼球+對深近視散光度數會冇咁準(依我理解)<br />\n但做完就唔使好似lasik咁驚青<br />\n所以你冇散光的話 我自己建議你做smile<br />\n你呢個度數應該算係好穩定易做易清哂"},{"pid":"1910bf261c6182ce5f7a0c263ceb09eeb964aa23","tid":2273114,"uid":292658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T11:51:25.000Z","msg":"I did in 養和 last year in november<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aec72479f0a779dc3a10d0370957e835cf49fb11","tid":2273114,"uid":140018,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T16:23:20.000Z","msg":"唔建議做，始終有風險，而且戴con 成本唔高，個人覺得醫生消防員都因為多少影響視力唔做，做咩咁博"}]}